response.overview: Lisa, Michael and Boris want to relax after a long week at work. But everything changes when an alien on board of a UFO suddenly lands and causes trouble in the neighborhood. Together with gas station cashier Daniela, they confront the uninvited guest so they can finally call it a day.
response.tagline: It came from space … to ruin their Friday!
response.title: Die Liga der außergewöhnlichen Arbeitnehmer
